{"tid":1557512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"旅遊業界發起慢駛遊行 促社會停止混亂","createTime":"2019-09-10T06:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T08:37:31.000Z","uid":122441,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e86606fa9f3ee00c45e8e1dfb89d616b8f706ff4","tid":1557512,"uid":122441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zg8uV6x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZg8uV6x.jpg&h=d8c602e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【Now新聞台】旅遊業界發起旅遊巴士慢駛遊行，抗議現時社會混亂，嚴重影響業界生計，呼籲政府協調銀行界延後旅遊巴供款。<br />\n<br />\n逾60架旅遊巴士由啟德承啟道出發，途經東區海底隧道、東區走廊及灣仔繞道，慢駛前往政府總部。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業界希望通過慢駛向社會表達盡快停止混亂及早重建經濟的訴求，又呼籲政府協調銀行界延後旅遊巴、的士及小巴等供款，舒緩中小企財政壓力。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業界憂慮示威持續會令旅行社及相連的行業倒閉，業界將有大批人失業。"},{"pid":"9983d8f0a3e72e5971386fd4739e8a4dc2d17917","tid":1557512,"uid":23392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ee9537977221bd6007ee0438b61fbeb30daea9","tid":1557512,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92b3680b9d59156a247c5d95487dd7a3f5c6bb0","tid":1557512,"uid":217275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5debdb4ceba3a3651a00741209ced11824e1c5","tid":1557512,"uid":55917,"like":2,"dislik